message.body: Hey mister mister. Any word on saturday night?
Or Saturday sunday in general? I have to RSVP for the party, that's why I asked. :)
I can't come on saturday because kt is going to be here but maybe next weekend??
Ok I'll let you know
Yeah I don't think I can come this weekend - u have school on monday or are u off for columbus day?
School on monday... :(
Womp womp, visit will happen another time! You have great weather for the move!
Yea unfortunate timing and awkward situation. Not like you could you could ask her to come a different weekend bc you are visiting me... I hope that becomes less so.
Yeah it just has taken so long to make this weekend thing happen so we best reschedule but I already have something to visit in philly!
What is it?
I think it's called the magic room??
And don't worry, I'm used to making room for princess...
What's the magic room?
Why didn't you arrange when school was going to start damnit???
It's some exhibit public space thing?
Oh I'm into that...
Are you moving tomorrow???
Yep! Feeling calm.
It is real lovely here so the timing is good!
Is it warm? Fall-USB?
Ugh fall-ish I mean
Yeah it's like 70s - colors haven't even started yet!
What?? They have here
Yeah not at all!
Oh. My. God. Straight up fried green tomatoes tonight. I just listened to adrian, the bouncer, talk about his life for 2 hours. We just got to 1985. This could
Be the best thing that's ever come out of pranna.
"The cats in philly are straight up murderers" - adrian
